        """
        Get a pair of PyCapsules containing a C ArrowArray representation of the object.

        Parameters
        ----------
        requested_schema : PyCapsule | None
            A PyCapsule containing a C ArrowSchema representation of a requested
            schema. Not supported.

        Returns
